#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.103"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.103:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.103:0.2"
msgid "11. Valāhakavagga"
msgstr "11. Clouds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.103:0.3"
msgid "103. Kumbhasutta"
msgstr "103. Pots"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.103:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, kumbhā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four pots."

msgctxt "an4.103:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

# I’ve reversed the sequence of each pair so they match with the explanations.
msgctxt "an4.103:1.3"
msgid "Tuccho pihito, pūro vivaṭo, tuccho vivaṭo, pūro pihito—"
msgstr ""
"~Covered but empty, ~uncovered but full, ~uncovered and empty, and ~covered "
"and full."

msgctxt "an4.103:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro kumbhā."
msgstr "These are the four pots."

msgctxt "an4.103:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro kumbhūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these four people similar to pots are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.103:1.6"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.103:1.7"
msgid "Tuccho pihito, pūro vivaṭo, tuccho vivaṭo, pūro pihito."
msgstr ""
"~Covered but empty, ~uncovered but full, ~uncovered and empty, and ~covered "
"and full."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.103:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo tuccho hoti pihito?"
msgstr "And how is a person covered but empty?"

msgctxt "an4.103:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person is impressive when going out and coming back, when "
"looking ahead and aside, when bending and extending the limbs, and when "
"bearing the outer robe, bowl and robes."

msgctxt "an4.103:2.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr ""
"But they don’t truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin "
"of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"leading to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "an4.103:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo tuccho hoti pihito."
msgstr "That’s how a person is covered but empty."

msgctxt "an4.103:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, kumbho tuccho pihito;"
msgstr "That person is like a pot that’s covered but empty, I say."

msgctxt "an4.103:2.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.103:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo pūro hoti vivaṭo?"
msgstr "And how is a person uncovered but full?"

msgctxt "an4.103:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.103:3.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "But they truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.103:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo pūro hoti vivaṭo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, kumbho pūro vivaṭo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:3.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.103:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo tuccho hoti vivaṭo?"
msgstr "And how is a person uncovered and empty?"

msgctxt "an4.103:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa na pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ "
"paṭikkantaṃ ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ "
"saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.103:4.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti."
msgstr "Nor do they truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.103:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo tuccho hoti vivaṭo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:4.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, kumbho tuccho vivaṭo;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:4.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.105"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.103:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo pūro hoti pihito?"
msgstr "And how is a person covered and full?"

msgctxt "an4.103:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa puggalassa pāsādikaṃ hoti abhikkantaṃ paṭikkantaṃ "
"ālokitaṃ vilokitaṃ samiñjitaṃ pasāritaṃ saṅghāṭipattacīvaradhāraṇaṃ."
msgstr "It’s when a person is impressive …"

msgctxt "an4.103:5.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr "And they truly understand: ‘This is suffering’ …"

msgctxt "an4.103:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo pūro hoti pihito."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:5.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, kumbho pūro pihito;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:5.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.103:5.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro kumbhūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These four people similar to pots are found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.103:5.8"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
